#     prime time 
def prime_t(x):
    if x in [10,11,12,13,14,15]:
        x = ''
    elif x in [16,17,18]:
        x = ''
    elif x in [21,22,23]:
        x = ''
    elif x in [0,1]:
        x = ''
    else:
        x = 'no_prime'
    return x
    
performance_data['prime_time'] = performance_data['hour'].apply(lambda x: prime_t(x))

group 시간대별¶

In [103]:
def add(x):
    return x['start_time']+datetime.timedelta(minutes = x['()'])
In [104]:
def group(df):
    df_sort =  df.copy()
    df_sort['index'] = df_sort.index   #  
    df_sort = df_sort.sort_values(['','']).reset_index(drop=True)
    
    df_sort['start_time'] = df_sort['']
    df_sort['end_time'] = df_sort[['()','start_time']].apply(add, axis=1)
    df_sort['group']=1
    
    for i in range(len(df_sort)-1):
        if (df_sort[''][i] == df_sort[''][i+1] and df_sort['end_time'][i] ==df_sort['start_time'][i+1]):
            df_sort['group'][i+1] = df_sort['group'][i]+1
            
    df_sort = df_sort.sort_values(['index']).reset_index(drop=True)
    return df_sort['group']
